news.headline: Stocks of Wall Street giants plunge as Trump tariff turmoil roils the finance world
news.summary: Stocks of the biggest banks and private-equity firms plunged Thursday as concerns mounted about how Wall Street giants and their customers might be affected by heightened odds of a US recession.
